{"sections": {"main": {"type": "main-product--default", "blocks": {"header": {"type": "product_header", "settings": {"show_divider": true, "show_vendor": true, "show_sku": true, "show_discount": true, "discount_format": "percent_off", "show_product_rating": false, "show_sale_badge": true, "show_custom_badges": true}}, "description": {"type": "description", "settings": {"title": "", "title_tag": "h3", "text_font_class": "fs-body-100", "column_placement": "right", "display_as_collapsible_row": false, "expand_by_default": false, "icon": "none"}}, "variant_picker": {"type": "variant_picker", "settings": {"variant_popup_option": "Size", "variant_popup_icon": "none", "variant_popup_text": "Size guide", "variant_popup_page": "", "swatch_size": "medium", "chip_layout": "natural"}}, "buy_buttons": {"type": "buy_buttons", "settings": {"show_dynamic_checkout": true, "enable_sticky_atc_bar_desktop": true, "enable_sticky_atc_bar_mobile": true, "divider_width": "border--thin"}}, "callouts": {"type": "product_callouts", "settings": {"title": "", "title_tag": "h3", "add_box": true, "add_dividers": true, "icon_1": "leaf", "text_1": "<p><strong>14k Gold</strong> \u00b7 Freshwater Pearls \u00b7 Diamond</p>", "icon_2": "measuring-tape", "text_2": "<p><strong>Asymmetric:</strong> Left 16\u00d712mm \u00b7 Right 10\u00d715mm</p>", "icon_3": "stiletto", "text_3": "<p>Handcrafted in NYC</p>", "icon_4": "moving-truck", "text_4": "<p>Free insured shipping \u00b7 1-year warranty</p>", "icon_5": "bill", "text_5": "<p><strong>Made to order</strong> \u00b7 3\u20134 week production</p>", "icon_6": "none", "text_6": "", "display_as_collapsible_row": false, "expand_by_default": false, "icon": "none"}}, "share": {"type": "share", "settings": {}}}, "block_order": ["header", "description", "variant_picker", "buy_buttons", "callouts", "share"], "settings": {"enable_sticky_product_details": true, "show_breadcrumbs": false, "show_navigation_buttons": false, "auto_collapse_rows": false, "show_featured_media_first": false, "gallery_style": "list", "gallery_style_mobile": "carousel", "gallery_size": "large", "gallery_overflow": "3", "enable_video_looping": true, "enable_product_lightbox": true, "image_aspect_ratio": "portrait", "enable_multiple_variant_media": false, "enable_mobile_carousel_looping": true, "show_mobile_carousel_images_full_width": true, "hide_mobile_carousel_dots": false, "enable_gift_card_recipient": true, "enable_animation": true}}, "product_tabs": {"type": "product-tabs", "blocks": {"tab_description": {"type": "one_column", "settings": {"tab_heading": "Description", "heading_column_1": "What Makes It Special", "heading_font_class_column_1": "fs-heading-4-base", "heading_tag_column_1": "h3", "text_column_1": "<p>Organic gold branches stretch and shift with natural rhythm, punctuated by luminous pearls and a distant glimmer of diamond \u2014 like a constellation traced in gold.</p><p>Lyra is intentionally asymmetrical. The left ear gets a wider, more grounded form; the right, a taller, reaching silhouette. Worn together they create a visual harmony that's more interesting than perfect symmetry. The 0.03ct diamond catches light unexpectedly \u2014 a tiny flash you'll notice in mirrors.</p>", "page_for_content_column_1": "", "custom_liquid_column_1": "", "text_font_class_column_1": "fs-body-100", "content_width": "custom", "text_max_width": 800, "image_width_column_1": 100, "image_position_column_1": "above_text"}}, "tab_details": {"type": "one_column", "settings": {"tab_heading": "Details & Materials", "heading_column_1": "Specifications", "heading_font_class_column_1": "fs-heading-4-base", "heading_tag_column_1": "h3", "text_column_1": "<ul><li><strong>Material:</strong> 14k yellow gold</li><li><strong>Stones:</strong> Freshwater pearls (4.5mm \u00d7 2, 3mm \u00d7 2), diamond (0.03 ct total)</li><li><strong>Dimensions:</strong> Left 16 \u00d7 12mm, Right 10 \u00d7 15mm (asymmetrical)</li><li><strong>Weight:</strong> Light enough for all-day wear</li><li><strong>Closure:</strong> Post with butterfly back</li><li><strong>Collection:</strong> Echoes</li></ul>", "page_for_content_column_1": "", "custom_liquid_column_1": "", "text_font_class_column_1": "fs-body-100", "content_width": "custom", "text_max_width": 800, "image_width_column_1": 100, "image_position_column_1": "above_text"}}, "tab_care": {"type": "one_column", "settings": {"tab_heading": "Care", "heading_column_1": "Jewelry Care", "heading_font_class_column_1": "fs-heading-4-base", "heading_tag_column_1": "h3", "text_column_1": "<p><strong>Gold & Pearl Pieces:</strong> Put jewelry on last, take it off first. Wipe with a soft cloth after wearing. Store in the provided pouch. Avoid perfume, chlorine, and harsh chemicals. Pearls benefit from being worn \u2014 natural skin oils maintain their luster.</p>", "page_for_content_column_1": "", "custom_liquid_column_1": "", "text_font_class_column_1": "fs-body-100", "content_width": "custom", "text_max_width": 800, "image_width_column_1": 100, "image_position_column_1": "above_text"}}, "tab_shipping": {"type": "two_column_tab", "settings": {"tab_heading": "Shipping & Returns", "content_vertical_alignment": "top", "column_spacing": 48, "heading_column_1": "Made to Order", "heading_font_class_column_1": "fs-heading-4-base", "heading_tag_column_1": "h3", "text_column_1": "<p>Every piece is handcrafted to order in NYC. Please allow 3\u20134 weeks for production. Free insured shipping on all orders. Signature required on delivery. You'll receive email updates during production and tracking when your piece ships.</p>", "page_for_content_column_1": "", "custom_liquid_column_1": "", "text_font_class_column_1": "fs-body-100", "image_width_column_1": 100, "image_position_column_1": "above_text", "heading_column_2": "Returns & Warranty", "heading_font_class_column_2": "fs-heading-4-base", "heading_tag_column_2": "h3", "text_column_2": "<p>All sales are final \u2014 each piece is made specifically for you. 1-year warranty covers manufacturing defects. If your piece arrives damaged, contact us within 14 days with photos for repair or replacement.</p>", "page_for_content_column_2": "", "custom_liquid_column_2": "", "text_font_class_column_2": "fs-body-100", "image_width_column_2": 100, "image_position_column_2": "above_text"}}}, "block_order": ["tab_description", "tab_details", "tab_care", "tab_shipping"], "settings": {"tab_alignment": "left", "tab_spacing": 40, "font_choice": "ff-heading", "tab_font_size": "fs-body-150", "auto_collapse_rows": false, "background_color": "", "text_color": "#000000", "enable_animation": true, "section_padding": "section--vertical-padding-bottom-only"}}, "multi-column": {"type": "multi-column", "blocks": {}, "block_order": [], "disabled": true, "settings": {"title": "", "heading_tag": "h2", "heading_font_class": "fs-heading-3-base", "subheading": "", "heading_alignment": "left", "content_vertical_alignment": "center", "content_background_padding": "large", "columns": "3", "column_spacing": 4, "row_spacing": 28, "column_alignment": "center", "enable_slider_mobile": false, "columns_mobile": "1", "column_spacing_mobile": 4, "row_spacing_mobile": 4, "column_alignment_mobile": "center", "background_behind_columns": false, "background_color": "#f5f3f0", "text_color": "#3d352f", "button_background_color": "#000000", "button_text_color": "#ffffff", "enable_animation": true, "divider_style": "none", "section_padding": "section--vertical-padding-top-bottom"}}, "image-hero": {"type": "image-hero", "blocks": {"accent": {"type": "accent", "settings": {"accent": "ECHOES COLLECTION"}}, "heading": {"type": "heading", "settings": {"title": "Lyra", "heading_tag": "h2", "heading_font_class": "fs-heading-display-2"}}}, "block_order": ["accent", "heading"], "settings": {"image_aspect": "custom", "desktop_height": 60, "mobile_height": 65, "focal_point": "center", "mobile_focal_point": "center", "media_link": "", "text_position": "flex-end_flex-end", "text_position_mobile": "center_center", "text_color": "#f5f5f5", "button_background_color": "#ffffff", "button_text_color": "#000000", "color_overlay": "#000000", "color_overlay_gradient": "", "overlay_opacity": 25, "enable_animation": true, "section_padding": "section--vertical-padding-none"}}, "testimonials": {"type": "testimonials", "blocks": {"review-1": {"type": "testimonial", "settings": {"product": "lyra", "image_position": "right", "aspect_ratio": "square", "focal_point": "image_presentation", "show_rating": true, "rating": 5, "quote": "The asymmetry is everything. They look like tiny sculptures. I wore them to a gallery opening and the artist asked where I got them.", "author": "\u2013 Margot L. \u00b7 Verified Buyer"}}, "review-2": {"type": "testimonial", "settings": {"product": "lyra", "image_position": "right", "aspect_ratio": "square", "focal_point": "image_presentation", "show_rating": true, "rating": 5, "quote": "That little diamond \u2014 you can't see it from far away but when you catch it in sunlight it's this gorgeous surprise. Obsessed.", "author": "\u2013 Deepa S. \u00b7 Verified Buyer"}}, "review-3": {"type": "testimonial", "settings": {"product": "lyra", "image_position": "right", "aspect_ratio": "square", "focal_point": "image_presentation", "show_rating": true, "rating": 5, "quote": "I was nervous about asymmetric earrings but they balance each other perfectly. More interesting than matching pairs.", "author": "\u2013 Hannah R. \u00b7 Verified Buyer"}}, "review-4": {"type": "testimonial", "settings": {"product": "lyra", "image_position": "right", "aspect_ratio": "square", "focal_point": "image_presentation", "show_rating": true, "rating": 4, "quote": "Exquisite work. Took about 3.5 weeks but the quality speaks for itself. The gold has a beautiful warm tone.", "author": "\u2013 Yuki N. \u00b7 Verified Buyer"}}}, "block_order": ["review-1", "review-2", "review-3", "review-4"], "settings": {"image_size": "small", "quote_font": "body", "background_color": "#fcfcf9", "text_col